cterised by a line width of full width\nhalf max FWHM > 700 km/s. Furthermore, we find a sub-sample of 12 sources the\nstack of which maximises the broad component emission. The stack of this\nsub-sample shows an excess emission due to a broad component of 1.2-2.5 sigma.\nThe stacked line of these sources has a broad component of FWHM > 775 km/s.\nDeeper ALMA observations are necessary to confirm the presence of a broad\ncomponent in the individual spectra.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Aug 2019 18:00:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-23"}
