, we investigate the\nrelative impact of HMXB feedback and stellar winds on our results, finding the\nubiquity of stellar winds throughout each starburst makes them a defining\nfactor in the final state of the interstellar medium.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 30 Aug 2019 06:41:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-02"}
