icability of such a transfer by using it to derive results for certain\ntypes of varieties from properties of bounded distributive lattices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 30 Aug 2019 12:27:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 18 Nov 2019 21:13:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-20"}
